HEADWORD: Interruptedly
<hw>In`ter*rupt"ed*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>With breaks or
interruptions; discontinuously.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Interruptedly pinnate</b></col> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>,
<cd>pinnate with small leaflets intermixed with large ones.</cd>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

